## Task 5: Model Recommendation
# Recommended Model

Transformer-Based NLP Model (BERT)

# Why BERT is Suitable

BERT is one of the most effective NLP models for understanding human language and context. Unlike traditional models, BERT can understand the meaning of words based on surrounding text, which improves sentiment prediction accuracy.

For example, it can better understand sentences like:

“The product quality is good but delivery was very slow.”

This makes it highly useful for customer review analysis.

# Benefits of Using BERT
Better understanding of customer language
High accuracy in sentiment prediction
Ability to process large amounts of text
Improved contextual understanding

# Alternative Models

Other models that can also be used:

LSTM
RNN
Logistic Regression with TF-IDF
DistilBERT for faster performance

